<td class="roundytr" style="background:#FFF"> <a href="/wiki/Bill_(Adventures)" title="Bill (Adventures)">Bill</a>
</td></tr></table>
<p><b>Bill</b> (Japanese: <b>ソネザキマサキ</b> <i>Masaki Sonezaki</i>) is a <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_(species)" title="Pokémon (species)">Pokémon</a> Researcher, widely regarded as an expert in many fields. He has made many appearances in the games. Bill is most commonly found in his <a href="/wiki/Sea_Cottage" title="Sea Cottage">Sea Cottage</a>, which is north of <a href="/wiki/Cerulean_City" title="Cerulean City">Cerulean City</a> at the end of <a href="/wiki/Kanto_Route_25" title="Kanto Route 25">Route 25</a>. He is most notable for his first appearance in the <a href="/wiki/Generation_I" title="Generation I">Generation I</a> games and for his <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Storage_System" title="Pokémon Storage System">Pokémon Storage System</a> that has been pertinent in the entire main series.
</p>
