<dd><i>"My pop, he won't work. All he does is goof off all day long. He's getting to be a real headache..."</i><b><sup><a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Crystal_Version" title="Pokémon Crystal Version"><span style="color:#4FD9FF;">C</span></a></sup></b></dd></dl>
