<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Generation_VII"><a href="/wiki/Generation_VII" title="Generation VII">Generation VII</a></span></h3>
<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Alola">Alola</span></h4>
<p>Although he has no physical appearance in <a href="/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Sun_and_Moon_Versions" class="mw-redirect" title="Pokémon Sun and Moon Versions">Pokémon Sun and Moon</a>, <a href="/wiki/Lillie" title="Lillie">Lillie</a> goes to him to treat <a href="/wiki/Lusamine" title="Lusamine">her mother</a>, even making a reference to when he was combined with a <a href="/wiki/Clefairy_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Clefairy (Pokémon)">Clefairy</a>.
</p>
