<td>From 正木 <i>masaki</i> (<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Euonymus_japonicus" class="extiw" title="wp:Euonymus japonicus">Japanese spindle</a>) and possibly みさき <i>misaki</i> (cape), referring to where he lives.
</td></tr>
